Comment:
I've decided to annotate this game for a number of reasons. Firstly it's between it's against an opponent 100 points north of my rating. It's from a Kings Gambit tournament and after the game ended, he was top of the ranking  with 11 points and I was joint next to bottom with 2. This is a fairly short game (22 moves) and the analysis suggests a total of only one inaccuracy, two mistakes and a single blunder which suggests to me that the game was fairly close overall

I wanted to try this tournament as even though most opponents are higher ranked than me I though it would be interesting and that has certainly proved to be the case.
